Package clients

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    E2EValidationClient
    the client used to execute E2EValidationRequest and also can be single instated to handle a end to end validation
    EmailClient
    the client used to execute EmailRequest and also can be single instated to send an email
    PSClient
    the client used to execute a CommandRequest which belongs to PowserShell and also can be single instated to handle PowserShell command
    RestfClient
    the client used to execute a RestfRequest and also can be single instated to handle Restf web service Request Some properites like proxy you can configured in the file which path is "%userprofile%\.rest-client\rest-client.properties", that file will be generated after you executed a request on time.
    ScenarioClient
    the client used to execute a ScenarioRequest and also can be single instated to handle a class extends Scenario
    SQLClient
    the client used to execute a CommandRequest which belongs to oracle's SQL and also can be single instated to handle oracle's SQL
    SSHClient
    the client used to execute a CommandRequest which belongs to SSH command and also can be single instated to handle SSH command
